Summary

Dataset: Bangladesh

Outcome: Emergent Literacy (expressvocab1 - oralcomp5)

Comparison variable: Gender (female, male)

Items with no variance: none

Items with no variance within levels of comparison variable: none

Bias detection method: IRT

Total number of biased items: 2 out of 24

Type of item bias: non-uniform
